name: Studies in Shakespeare
description: A study of the plays of Shakespeare. An in-depth study of select plays from Shakespeare's dramatic corpus combined with an introduction to the critical debates within Shakespeare studies. Students will gain a richer understanding of Shakespeare's texts and their critical reception.Pre-1900 course
prerequisites: [ENGB03H3 and ENGB04H3 and one of ENGB05H3 or (ENGB01H3) or (ENGB10H3)]] and [ENGB32H3 or ENGB33H3]
